  dayNarratives:
  - day: 1
    narrativeOpen: "March 14, 2187. You officially begin your post as Customs Inspector
      at Olympus Station.\n\nThe station chief hands you an ARGUS R7 operator's manual
      \u2014 large sections have been redacted by the military.\n\n\"Don't worry
      about the black bars,\" he says. \"Just follow protocol. Two ships docking
      today, both regulars.\"\n\nYou power on the terminal and face the four-quadrant
      readout for the first time."
    narrativeCloseDefault: 'A quiet day. You power down the terminal, thinking this
      job might not be so hard after all.


      But you notice the lights in the
      adjacent security bay keep flickering.'
    narrativeCloseCaught: 
    narrativeCloseMissed: 
    manifestDisplayText: "\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\nARGUS
