    manifest:
    - shipId: K-002
      intent: RESUPPLY
    - shipId: K-008
      intent: OFFLOAD
  - day: 2
    narrativeOpen: "Early morning. Lena, the comms officer, leans in and whispers:\n\n\"Last
      night we intercepted a strange signal on the outer channel... the format was
      identical to our ARGUS encoding, but the source is unknown.\"\n\nShe trails
      off and returns to her station without another word.\n\nThree ships today \u2014
      you're starting to think those redacted sections in the manual might not be
      \"irrelevant\" after all."
    narrativeCloseDefault: 'Your judgment was spot on today. But before clocking
      out, Lena leaves a note on your desk:


      "Watch the COMMS column. Some
      things... shouldn''t be that color."'
    narrativeCloseCaught: 'You denied a suspicious vessel. The security alarm triggered
      briefly, then everything went quiet.


      No one told you what happened.
      But you saw military personnel hurrying down the corridor.'
    narrativeCloseMissed: 'You cleared all ships. That night, a strange metallic
      scraping echoed from the far end of the corridor.


      The next morning,
      a cleaning bot found unidentified organic residue in Cargo Bay C-7.'
    manifestDisplayText: "\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\nARGUS
      TERMINAL R7   DAILY SCHEDULED ARRIVALS \u2014 DAY 2\n\nROUTE: KILO\nISSUED:
