    - shipId: K-004
      intent: EMERGENCY
  - day: 4
    narrativeOpen: "The station has entered partial lockdown. Armed patrols are now
      deployed across the port district.\n\nThe chief calls you into his office:\n\n\"Starting
      today, you examine every ship carefully. Every quadrant. I can't tell you why
      \u2014 but if you let in something that shouldn't be here, the consequences...\"\n\nHe
      doesn't finish the sentence.\n\nYou return to your terminal. Three ships today,
      and all you have is a half-redacted manual."
    narrativeCloseDefault: 'Precise judgment. You''re beginning to understand the
      logic behind those redacted rules.


      You can even start predicting which
      combinations are ''impossible in nature.'''
    narrativeCloseCaught: "You flagged another suspicious vessel. This time you saw
      it yourself \u2014\n\nAs the denied ship undocked, something was writhing in
      the gap between its hatch doors. Not a mechanical malfunction.\n\nIt was alive."
    narrativeCloseMissed: "Another ship entered the port without thorough inspection.\n\nLate
      that night, a piercing alarm blared from Sector D \u2014 it lasted three seconds
      before being force-muted.\n\nThe next day, Sector D was sealed off entirely
      by the military."
    manifestDisplayText: "\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\nARGUS
      TERMINAL R7   DAILY SCHEDULED ARRIVALS \u2014 DAY 4\n\nROUTE: KILO\nISSUED:
