  - day: 5
    narrativeOpen: "The last day.\n\nAt 0400 hours, the broadcast system played an
      encrypted message \u2014 but the encryption seemed to 'accidentally' fail,
      and everyone heard it:\n\n\"...MIMIC protocol activated... port isolation countdown
      18 hours... all unverified biological entities will be...\"\n\nThe signal cut
      out there.\n\nYou sit at your terminal. Three more ships. You know what you
      have to do.\n\nThose redacted sections in the manual \u2014 you've worked out
      all of them by now.\n\nOr at least, you hope you have."
    narrativeCloseDefault: 
    narrativeCloseCaught: 
    narrativeCloseMissed: 
